rComments: Really sweet and funny! Made lectures actually enjoyable (he even rapped for us after the last class). He seemed a little awkward but he knew his content and was great at explaining things. His tests and assignments were not too challenging

Dr. Welch is truly an "academic eccentric" but I love that. He really cares about his students and is always available. His lectures are super clear and he grades fairly. I will definitely take again if I can.

Great at explaining the concepts in lecture, such that the textbook is mostly not needed cept for clarification. He cares about his students, if you go up to him after lecture he will certainly talk to you.  Knowledgeable, deeply caring and interested in what he's teaching,  a bit eccentric, and an all around great person. 11/10 would take again.
